data.description: Immediate possession! +Home Protection Warranty paid thru 10/2025. Home offers 3 total bedrooms (one on main and two upstairs), one full bathroom, main floor laundry, stainless steel kitchen appliances, including a dishwasher installed new in 7/2022. Screened three season porch on front of home. Fenced back yard. All appliances included w/ home, including washer and dryer. Home sits near the end of of cul de sac (no through traffic) and offers easy access to highway, bus routes, schools, and shopping or local conveniences. Currently registered with city of GR as rental property with approved Certificate of Compliance in place. Note: Listing agent has ownership interest in property. Seller is a licensed real estate salesperson in the state of MI. Seller has never lived in property.  BTVAI
